{"tid":1260491,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"圍狗總有咩用？","createTime":"2019-06-27T00:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T13:57:16.000Z","uid":222592,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c387e944ab8bd0746e36c7e67b4c2158546607c0","tid":1260491,"uid":222592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T00:33:25.000Z","msg":"明眼人都知風向變緊<br />\n已經冇左之前一面倒個樣野<br />\n共產黨最叻其中一招就係分化<br />\n等敵人自己內鬥<br />\n<br />\n其實局勢好簡單 <br />\n1. 警犬 / 2.一般民眾 / 3.熱血青年<br />\n<br />\n1同3人數最少 但對立得好緊要<br />\n只要其中一方過火左 就會失去2支持<br />\n咁依場運動就收皮 <br />\n<br />\n大量三毛係連登做緊野 <br />\n大多數都係鼓吹情緒<br />\n<br />\n目的得一個<br />\n就係想你地自己圍爐 打飛機<br />\n跟住就失去理智 <br />\n做出過火野失去民眾支持<br />\n<br />\n可能你會問咁下一步可以做咩<br />\n其實我都唔撚知 但希望大家可以保持理智<br />\n<br />\n利申：一名不勇武的毒撚"},{"pid":"285893a598c1811ebef2d0f40c14ecc1370ec8b3","tid":1260491,"uid":222592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T00:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1db1595e9ec6a628085717d01ec62b9bafa3030","tid":1260491,"uid":222592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981122dcbdd2ebaff1f5d0659bef2cd10ad2101c","tid":1260491,"uid":157994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:19:04.000Z","msg":"去律政有幾理智 你知唔知勇武用處係邊緣武力度？"},{"pid":"cc0eab452df9a9fd6412336986f61d4321aba102","tid":1260491,"uid":222592,"